  "body": "Currently a balance is of type Gwei, 1ETH is tracked as 1_000_000_000 and as a bigint.\r\n\r\nWe can track balance as a number for faster processing and for saving memory too, because it's unlikely that a validator balance has more than 9M ETH as calculated below\r\n\r\n```\r\n> 2 ** 53 / 1000000000\r\n9007199.254740993\r\n```",
